==Description==

The '''Std AnnotationLabel''' command creates an annotation label in the [[3D_View|3D View]].

[[Image:Std_Annotation_label_example.PNG|400px]]

{{Caption|Example of annotation label}}

==Usage==

# Select a geometric entity in the [[3D_View|3D View]].
# Select the {{MenuCommand|Tools → [[Image:Std_AnnotationLabel.svg|16px]] Annotation Label}} option from the menu.
# Annotation label will be added to 3D View at the selected location. The corresponding ''Label'' object will be added to the [[Tree_View|Tree View]].
# Change the ''Label Text'' property to set the label text.
# Optionally, change the View properties to modify the appearance of the label. 



